data.description: ! Seller offering buyers pick of 2-1 buydown OR 10k concession !    This stunning 4-bedroom, 2 full bathroom home is located in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Mason Hill, nestled in between the historical charm of Georgetown and the vibrant energy of North Austin. Boasting a spacious and inviting layout, this home exudes elegance and charm. The oversize island kitchen is perfect for cooking, eating, and entertaining, with a cozy brick fireplace that provides a warm and welcoming ambiance to the living space. Step outside to your own private oasis in the backyard and enjoy relaxing on the covered patio. This community offers endless amenities, including hiking and jogging trails, parks, pools with splashpads, a fitness center, and fishing ponds - all of which provide resort-style living without the hefty price tag. This home has been lovingly cared for and is just waiting for the perfect buyers to make it their own. Home includes a tankless water heater. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this gem your new home!
